    "causal_summary": "This phase ports CocoIndex's statediff model into Spec Kit Memory as a storage reconciliation layer. The current system has several reconciliation fragments: scan categorization, stale cleanup, alias divergence handling, embedding cache writes, FTS and BM25 updates, causal graph mutation, and post-mutation cache hooks. They should not all remain inline branches inside handlers.",
